headline: KeyBank and the Buffalo Sabres Announce 10-Year Extension of Arena Naming Rights Deal
summary: BUFFALO, NY / ACCESS Newswire / August 7, 2025 / KeyBank KeyBank(NYSE:KEY) and theBuffalo Sabrestoday announced a 10-year extension of their arena naming rights deal. The contract, which is set to begin in 2026-27, will keep the KeyBank Center name ...
